  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0ba3\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b9a\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b95\u0ba8\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A suspect who was part of the money counting team at the Presidential Palace was arrested",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "A 26-year-old man has been arrested on suspicion of damaging property at the President's official residence during the recent popular protests in Colombo.",
        "The police said that the young man was arrested on suspicion of causing damage to property after the public besieged the President's residence on the 9th.",
        "The suspect arrested this morning has been identified as a resident of Colombo 14, Mal Mawatha. He is said to be working at a shop in Husenia Street, Colombo.",
        "The suspect has been identified as a member of a group that was counting money found at the President's official residence after the public besieged the government building.",
        "It is noteworthy that the president was identified after a video footage of a group of protesters counting money found at his official residence was shared on social media."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
